{"tid":217723,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打絲打住珀麗灣？請入一入","createTime":"2017-04-26T03:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T09:29:54.000Z","uid":32213,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"482a30d84deafc33b33a11a4e1b38b720d6e3fe9","tid":217723,"uid":32213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T03:54:05.000Z","msg":"見珀麗灣好似幾幽靜<br />\n想買果度住<br />\n但見到有住客投訴飛機嘈音好曬利<br />\n<br />\n有冇依家住果度嘅巴打絲打講下分享下嘈唔嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇其他問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n交通直覺還可以頂得順"},{"pid":"aab5eabd922b536c7b1396fb0db79fd767909187","tid":217723,"uid":32213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T03:54:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23fe93701dc79079c7e7df37bf7be8fd0cfb5477","tid":217723,"uid":66395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:12:06.000Z","msg":"飛機好撚近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7222583274a7f3a6ec1835080189dbeb89d392e5","tid":217723,"uid":32213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T12:55:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飛機好撚近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你住果度？"},{"pid":"797c3e628ddc266f3a37656df58937442f775041","tid":217723,"uid":6211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T09:00:01.000Z","msg":"住耐左唔覺<br />\n不過呢D睇人"},{"pid":"dc32c809d0fde14aea4db6f2b4b9d8218a354a69","tid":217723,"uid":39922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T09:03:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0068ed2e6698e447c26f97beb418f7e111de2849","tid":217723,"uid":65745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T09:12:25.000Z","msg":"之前住一期中層望內園唔覺飛機聲好嘈，住三期望村屋向住馬路d巴士重撚嘈"},{"pid":"e0b8264c59b489754718bfcb8aee35befe10abf8","tid":217723,"uid":57505,